<main id="faq-page">
    <section class="faq-section">
        <h1 class="faq-main-heading">
            Frequently asked
            <span class="highlight">questions</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="faq-sub-heading">Do you need some help with something or do you have questions on some features ?</p>
        <div class="accordion-container">
            <details class="accordion-item">
                <summary class="accordion-header">
                    How do I place an order?
                    <span class="icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="ri-add-line plus-icon"></i>
                        <i class="ri-subtract-line minus-icon"></i>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>Simply browse our products, add your desired items to the cart, and proceed to checkout. Follow the on-screen instructions to complete your purchase securely.</p>
                </div>
            </details>
            <details class="accordion-item">
                <summary class="accordion-header">
                    What payment methods do you accept?
                    <span class="icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="ri-add-line plus-icon"></i>
                        <i class="ri-subtract-line minus-icon"></i>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>We accept all major credit and debit cards, PayPal, and select digital wallets. All payments are processed securely for your peace of mind.</p>
                </div>
            </details>
            <details class="accordion-item">
                <summary class="accordion-header">
                    How can I track my order?
                    <span class="icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="ri-add-line plus-icon"></i>
                        <i class="ri-subtract-line minus-icon"></i>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>Once your order is shipped, you will receive a confirmation email with a tracking link. You can also track your order status in your account dashboard.</p>
                </div>
            </details>
            <details class="accordion-item">
                <summary class="accordion-header">
                    What is your return and refund policy?
                    <span class="icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="ri-add-line plus-icon"></i>
                        <i class="ri-subtract-line minus-icon"></i>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>We offer a 14-day return policy on most items. If you are not satisfied with your purchase, contact our support team to initiate a return or exchange. Refunds are processed within 3-5 business days after receiving the returned item.</p>
                </div>
            </details>
            <details class="accordion-item">
                <summary class="accordion-header">
                    How do I contact customer support?
                    <span class="icon-wrapper">
                        <i class="ri-add-line plus-icon"></i>
                        <i class="ri-subtract-line minus-icon"></i>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                    <p>You can reach our customer support team via the Contact page, email, or live chat. We are here to help you with any questions or concerns you may have.</p>
                </div>
            </details>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>
